title: International Cup 2025 dates set
content: The 2025 Lansdowne International Cup will be held from Oct.17 to Oct 18th.

title: Registration Now Open
content: Registration for the International Cup 2025 is now open. Don't miss your chance to be part of this exciting tournament!

title: Team Captains Announced
content: We're excited to announce the team captains for the 2025 International Cup. Both Team USA and Team International have selected experienced leaders.
